{
  "stem": "9538.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] In February of '42, there was a notice pinned up on, on the-- on the-- on the walls of the ghetto that the conditions are very bad in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "See, elderly people should volunteer to go, to be taken away from the ghetto to Dunamunde, which is the town that is the estuary of the-- of the Duna, which is the river which flows through Riga.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they should work in the fish-canning factory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There, they will have plenty to eat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They will be in warm billets.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they shall have it very good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But only the elderly should volunteer, which they did.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They registered.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And two days later, of course, they had to assemble-- what we called the Appellplatz, which is a big marketplace in the ghetto of Riga where the hangings and shootings and everything took place.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They had to assemble there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were registered.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And lorries came-- not these gray lorries, which were in Skirotava, other lorries-- looked more like furniture vans.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they went on it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we, from the nursing staff, you know, from the hospitals, we had to help the elderly people to get onto these lorries.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we were in the belief that they'll really go somewhere where they have it better than in the cold ghetto.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They were going to this fish-canning factory where they had to eat and where they were in a warm place.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But then afterwards, nearer the end of the-- this carried on the whole morning.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Quite a few thousand of them went.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Somebody tricked and said-- one of the Latvian Jews who was helping us and who was very familiar with the surrounding of Riga.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He was a native of Riga.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
